  "description": {
    "short": "Ask about deliveries, drivers, and routes",
    "full": "AI-powered dispatch assistant that manages EWM outbound deliveries, driver assignments, GPS tracking, and Google Maps routes. Powered by LangGraph and SAP AI Core Claude."
